If anyone finds this and looking for a way to pause a playing video you can reset the iframe src and it pauses. A poor man's video pause

    $('.slider__item.video_youtube iframe').attr('src', $('.slider__item.video_youtube iframe').attr('src'));
    $('.slider__item.video_mp4 iframe').attr('src', $('.slider__item.video_mp4 iframe').attr('src'));
